{
  "stem": "4284.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were supposed to build that little neighboring camp into something which we never did understand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We did-- we worked on fields.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was-- there seemed to be no rhyme and reason.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The one thing you notice, that the bunks you were on were all brand new, was all clean and new.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So something was in the works that we never came to understand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We did different types of work with lumber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And, and you can never quite figure out what's the purpose for which we're here, which made everybody a little bit nervous.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were told in the middle of January that we have to be on a collection place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we will have to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I find myself with many of others, not all 131 on them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were all separated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was disjointed, on what's finally considered to be a death march.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was wintertime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was snow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We had about 1,200 people assembled.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we marched off out of the camp under heavy guard with a very simple rule.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Whoever falls behind and creates a distance between the column and yourself will be shot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They had the jeep, like a personnel vehicle, with a machine gun, and officers, and soldiers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And you were heavily guarded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Not that you really had a chance to, to run anywhere, because you didn't have the strength.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You didn't have any direction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "You were certainly skinny, and recognized, and numbered, no hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I mean, there was no escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And off on the road, you had corpses by the dozen-- unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "There was an intimidating concern that you had not to end at the end of the column.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And it produced a remarkable speed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Because as everybody came behind, they now speed up.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
